Octinisept. Indications - treatment of skin and mucous membranes before diagnostic and surgical procedures in pediatric, surgical and obstetrics-gynecological practice, in traumatology, proctology, dermatovenerology, otorhinolaryngology, dentistry;
treatment of wound and burn surfaces; prophylaxis of foot mycosis and interfinger mycosis.
        In private cases it is recommended for hypertension and semi-fainting.
